总结：
1.选择
if/elif带有condition
     else无condition
     if
     elif
     elif
     ....
     else
 2.循环 while

一、Flow Control元素
1.condition
2.clause
 a block of code
 
二、if 
结构：
1.if condition 冒号
2.clause
例如：
print('What is your name?')
name = input()
if name == 'Alice':
  print('Hi, Alice.')
三、else
结构：
1.else 冒号
2.clause
例如：
print('What is your name?')
name = input()
if name == 'Alice':
  print('Hi Alice')
else:
  print('Hello, Stranger.')
  
三、elif                              #同else，上面的错了，才可以执行#当有多个elif时顺序很重要
结构：
1.elif condition 冒号
2.clause
例如：一个
if name == 'Alice':
  print('Hi Alice')
elif age > 12:
  print('You are not Alice')
                             #多个 age>2000放在100之后，就不会被执行
print('What is your name?')
name = input()
print('How old are you?')
age = int(input())
if name == 'Alice':
    print('Hi, Alice.')
elif age < 12:
    print('You are not Alice, kiddo.')
elif age > 2000:
    print('Unlike you, Alice is not an undead, immortal vampire.')   
elif age > 100:
    print('You are not Alice, grannie.')
    
四、while loop（循环）
结构
1.while condition 冒号
2.clause

name = ''      #目这一步的是为了进入循环
while name != 'your name':
    print('Please type your name.')
    name = input()
print('Thank you!')

while True:
    print('Please type your name.')
    name = input()
    if name == 'your name':
        break
print('Thank you!')
